'''LIRIC Associates''' was a [[computer security]] consultancy in the [[United Kingdom]] that offered risk and security assessment for global networks. It also provided advice on the design, architecture and policies required to secure complex global networks.  The company was a provider of Information Technology, IT Security and Telecommunications.  Its clients included UK government departments and private sector organizations.<ref>http://www.symantec.com/about/profile/development/acquisitions/</ref>

It was acquired by [[Symantec]] on September 17, 2004.<ref>{{cite web|accessdate=2008-04-15|url=http://www.symantec.com/press/2004/n040917.html|title= Symantec to Acquire LIRIC Associates|publisher=[[Symantec]]|date=2004-09-17}}</ref>

